# FlatProps

## Security Properties

Properties are security/correctness claims checked against function behavior.

| Property | Summary |
|----------|---------|
| [P1 — Hex](properties/misc.md#p1--hex) | Hex: asserts `0x7 == 0b0111`. |
| [P2 — Int](properties/misc.md#p2--int) | Int: asserts `291 == 0x00000123`. |
